Title: Aura — Hydration, intelligent.
Author: Cursor + Claude Code Skill
Draft date: 2026-06-20
Contact: https://www.aura-waters.com

=====

INT. VOID - CONTINUOUS

A dark blue void. A single drop of water falls in slow motion, catching light. Ripples expand outward in concentric circles, each ripple tinted with a soft aqua glow.

CUT TO:

INT. CLEAN STUDIO - DAY

The AURA bottle sits alone on a pedestal. Sleek glass, soft glow inside. Camera slowly pushes in.

CUT TO:

INT. BUSY OPEN-PLAN OFFICE - DAY

YOUNG PROFESSIONAL, late 20s, stares at a laptop. Eyes glazed. A glass of water sits untouched beside the keyboard. The clock shows 4:47 PM.

YOUNG PROFESSIONAL
(squinting)
I've been staring at this screen for six hours. I feel... foggy.

CUT TO:

INT. GYM - MORNING

A runner, mid-30s, in the middle of a workout. Breathing hard. Wipes forehead. Grabs a plain plastic bottle — empty.

RUNNER
(frustrated, breath)
Already out. Again.

CUT TO:

INT. LIBRARY - AFTERNOON

A STUDENT, early 20s, surrounded by textbooks. Three empty coffee cups. One untouched water bottle. Stands up, dizzy.

STUDENT
(confused)
Wait... when did I last drink water today?

CUT TO:

INT. VOID - CONTINUOUS

A grid of stats appears in white type, fading in one by one:

    75%  לא שותים מספיק מים ביום
    2.5L  הכמות המומלצת למבוגר
    3x   פעמים שכחנו לשתות השבוע

The numbers pulse, then shatter into pixels that drift toward camera.

CUT TO:

INT. CLEAN STUDIO - DAY

The AURA bottle, now CENTER FRAME. It catches light differently — there's a faint inner glow. The wordmark "Aura" materializes in soft aqua.

SMARTPHONE appears on the right side of frame, hovering. The screen is on, showing the AURA app home screen: a hydration ring at 18%.

A pulse of light travels from bottle to phone. The ring animates: 18% → 75% → 100%.

SMARTPHONE APP (V.O.)
(warm female voice, gentle)
Hi, Shay. I see you.

CUT TO:

INT. GYM - DAY

The runner is back. Same scene as before, but now the bottle has the AURA glow. S/he drinks. The bottle glows brighter with each sip.

SMARTPHONE APP (V.O.)
Great pace. 600ml so far today.

CUT TO:

INT. OPEN-PLAN OFFICE - DAY

The young professional again. Same scene — but now a soft blue glow on his wrist (smartwatch sync notification). He looks down, smiles slightly, picks up the AURA bottle, drinks.

SMARTPHONE APP (V.O.)
You crushed your morning target. Time for a refill.

CUT TO:

INT. LIBRARY - AFTERNOON

The student. Same scene — but now there are two empty water bottles, ONE AURA bottle half-empty, and she's studying calmly. Focus.

SMARTPHONE APP (V.O.)
You've been here 3 hours. Your focus score is up 34%.

CUT TO:

INT. VOID - CONTINUOUS

The AI Coach avatar appears. Soft circular design. Animated mouth as it speaks.

AI COACH
(encouraging, calm)
Hi. I'm your personal coach.
And I don't just remind you — I understand.

Three feature pills orbit the avatar:

    📊  מעקב חי
    🧠   AI מתאים אישית
    🔔   תזכורות חכמות

CUT TO:

INT. CLEAN STUDIO - DAY

The AURA bottle and smartphone side by side. The whole Aura logo appears large behind them. The world feels bigger — soft glow expanding outward.

A "Pre-order Now" CTA button pulses at the bottom of frame.

CTA (V.O.)
Join the waitlist. First shipment: July 2026.

WIDE SHOT:

The bottle floats in a soft blue pool of light. Website URL fades in:

    www.aura-waters.com

FADE TO:

INT. VOID - CONTINUOUS

The drop of water again — but this time, it doesn't fall. It hovers. The ripples are still expanding.

SMARTPHONE APP (V.O.)
(softly, almost a whisper)
You. Reimagined. Hydrated.

HOLD. FADE TO BLACK.

=====

THE END
